    <p><strong>Forno Bravo</strong> (independent California): Casa series modular dome, Professionale 110 and Professionale 130 traditional Naples-style, plus gas-assist variants on some Professionale models. American-made premium, parts via Forno Bravo direct. See <a href="/brands/forno-bravo-pizza-oven-repair/">Forno Bravo pizza oven repair</a>.</p>

